        dc:description           "Fig. 6. Map of Middle Eastern region of Colombia showing the geographic distribution of Trichomycterus steindachneri (circle): Cundinamarca, Ubaque, vereda Pueblo Nuevo, quebrada El Charco, 04°31’10.3”N 73°58’44.6”W, T. dorsostriatus (square): Meta, Villavicencio, 04°09’12”N 73°38’06”W and T. migrans (triangle): Meta, Serranía La Macarena, tributary creek of río Guayabero, 02°28’21”N 73°35’43”W. Inset at lower left corner corresponds to enlargment of distribution region of T. steindachneri." ;
